version=2

@Text.Show(The blackboard describes~Pokémon Status changes~during battles.*Which heading do you want~to read?)
@options.show(SLP,BRN,PSN,FRZ,PAR,Quit)

:when:SLP
@Text.Show(A Pokémon can't attack if~it's asleep!*Pokémon will stay asleep even~after battles!*Use Awakening to wake them~up!)

:when:BRN
@Text.Show(A burn reduces power and~speed. It also causes~ongoing damage.*Burns remain after battles.*Use Burn Heal to cure a~burn!)

:when:PSN
@Text.Show(When poisoned, a Pokémon's~health steadily drops.*Poison lingers after battles.*Use an Antidote to cure~poison!)

:when:FRZ
@Text.Show(If frozen, a Pokémon becomes~totally immobile!*It stays frozen even~after the battle ends.*Use Ice Heal to thaw~out Pokémon!)

:when:PAR
@Text.Show(Paralysis could make~Pokémon moves misfire!*Paralysis remains after battles.*Use Paralyz Heal for~treatment!)

:when:Quit
:end

:endwhen
:end